data.description: Welcome to an exquisite home nestled in the heart of French Country charm, where luxury & comfort converge in perfect harmony. This distinguished home offers an unparalleled blend of sophistication and tranquility, boasting 4 bedrooms & 4 baths amidst breathtaking natural surroundings. Beautiful hardwood flooring, complemented by vaulted ceilings adorned with rustic wood beams, & elegant crown molding create an ambiance of warmth. The focal point of the living room is a majestic fireplace that practically invites you to unwind in its comforting glow. Entertain with ease in the gourmet kitchen, where culinary dreams come to life with a Wolf cooktop, Kohler farmhouse sink, quartz countertops, & a convenient butler's pantry. From casual brunches to lavish dinner parties, every meal is a celebration of exquisite taste & refinement. Step outside to discover a haven of outdoor living, where a screened-in grilling porch beckons you to savor the flavors of the season amidst the tranquil beauty of nature. Gather around the outdoor gas fire pit under the starlit sky, sharing stories & laughter with loved ones against the backdrop of Craighead Forest Park, offering a seclusion. New roof 2023.
